export const formulaForcolumnOfFour = (boardSize: number) => boardSize * boardSize - (boardSize + boardSize + boardSize) - 1;
export const formulaForcolumnOfThree = (boardSize: number) => boardSize * boardSize - (boardSize + boardSize) - 1;
